theorem Topology.closure_interior_union_eq_closure_interiors
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A B : Set X} :
    closure (interior (A ∪ B)) = closure (interior A) ∪ closure (interior B) := by
  simpa [interior_union] using
    (Topology.closure_union_interiors_eq (A := A) (B := B))

theorem Topology.interior_union {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A B : Set X} :
    interior A ∪ interior B ⊆ interior (A ∪ B) := by
  intro x hx
  cases hx with
  | inl hA =>
      have h : interior A ⊆ interior (A ∪ B) :=
        interior_mono (Set.subset_union_left : A ⊆ A ∪ B)
      exact h hA
  | inr hB =>
      have h : interior B ⊆ interior (A ∪ B) :=
        interior_mono (Set.subset_union_right : B ⊆ A ∪ B)
      exact h hB

theorem Topology.closure_union_interiors_eq
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A B : Set X} :
    closure (interior A ∪ interior B) =
      closure (interior A) ∪ closure (interior B) := by
  simpa using closure_union (s := interior A) (t := interior B)

theorem Topology.closure_union_interiors_eq_union_closures
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A B : Set X} :
    closure (interior A ∪ interior B) =
      closure (interior A) ∪ closure (interior B) := by
  simpa using closure_union (s := interior A) (t := interior B)
